Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Problem Solver 68.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikuhachima speaking.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no job too big for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.75,0:00:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Background checks, armed security—\NWe'll do the crime if you got the dime.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.71,0:00:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.00,0:00:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We accept.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.76,0:00:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68 is happy to take on your request. {### tempted to drop PS68, but not 100% certain on doing that yet. Petz, thoughts?} {i vote keeping, people are going to hear the 68 in english. Though, in manga i probably would have done "We are ... " -rapid }
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane, isn't this...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.94,0:02:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.65,0:02:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We recovered this part from one of the \N{Kata Kata }Helmet Gang's armoured vehicles the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.28,0:02:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done some research, and I've found that \Nthis specific model is currently banned from use. {### In-game, it's mentioned that it's no longer in production, not that it's straight-up banned. TLC?} {yep its illegal to use it -rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.62,0:02:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could the Helmet Gang have gotten hold \Nof something illegal like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the Black Market?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.46,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, I feel like it would be difficult \Nfor them to secure such a large fleet that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.13,0:02:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure makes you wonder who's backing them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.64,0:02:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we look deeper into their supply route,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.31,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we may be able to find a lead on who's behind this. {### alt: "who the mastermind behind this is", "who's orchestrating this". It's a bit of a struggle with Teach, because idk if we wanna make him use "too big" words or not.} {imo "who's orchestrating this" sounds better even if its not direct it means the same thing --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.60,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. It might also reveal why \Nthey're specifically targeting our school. {maybe instead of "reveal" change to "shead light" --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.90,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.82,0:02:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With that out of the way, let's get back \Nto our regular meeting, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Our teacher{*Sensei} is present this time, {added alt track --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.70,0:03:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so make sure you're on your best behaviour.{### alt: "I'd appreciate a more serious conduct."}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.25,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Don't paint us as trouble students or anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasure to have ya, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise. Happy to be here. {"Likewise" feels redundant at best -- ik} {yeah you can just cut it --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with our plans going forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a suggestion, raise your hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, first-year Kuromi Serika{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.52,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As the treasurer of the Task Force,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.02,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to point out that our school \Nis on the verge of bankruptcy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.65,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only earn so much \Nfrom bounties and part-time gigs.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.66,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta go big or go home! {ok who the fuck actually says we got to to big or go home. I think "We gotta do something even bigger" works fine --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go big? How so? {if you change above change this to reflect that ==rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you asked!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, that's a pyramid scheme.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna profit from that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Say it ain't so... {I appreciate a Wheezer reference, but is this tone okay? -- ik} {WEEZER NOT WHEEZER --rapid} {also yeah no thats fucked make it "N- No way" or smth --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.31,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I already bought two bracelets...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our little Serika{**-chan} is so gullible.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just eat you up.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other suggestions?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.78,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Me, me, me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.94,0:04:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead, club president Hoshino. {### what is a more proper way to address these titles? She's using them to sound extra polite in the presence of Teach.} {Honestly, if we're going the route of "full title - name" then "president" could work fine here -- ik} {yeah just "President Hoshino" should work --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this. {## "why do I hear Unwelcome School playing?"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.78,Alt,,0,0,0,,Upsy daisy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One problem clearly overshadows the others:
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.79,0:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around. The entire student body \Nis currently here in this room!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.75,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More students means more student fees. {A bit liberal. Maybe "A school is only as strong as its student body" -- ik} { agree with ik, his tl should work --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.88,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our number one priority should be \Nto raise our student numbers!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.26,0:04:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Astute observation, but how would we do that? {While not incorrect, "astute" seems off here. I guess I always saw Ayane as more plain-spoken? -- ik} {yeah ayane yaps and uses lots of techical terms but doens't really speak too fancily shes not like posh or anything and astute give of a posh vibe literally "thats a nice observation" works better here --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple. {### alt: "It's elementary, my dear Ayane-chan." if we wanna ramp it up a tad} {I don't mind a good Sherlock Holmes reference myself -- ik} {i say fuck it we ball --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We abduct students from \Nanother school's school bus!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go busjacking?! {### https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/busjacking}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They either sign the transfer papers,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or they make the bus their new home! {### I need something punchier. Nazaki, thoughts?} {She says it quite matter of fact in the original, so injecting too much punch here is something I'd avoid personally -- ik} {this is fine as is imo, has the voice right and is accurate--rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.44,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom! Instant influx of new faces.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's genius.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who's our target? Trinity?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe Gehenna? Millenium?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.17,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourselves in their shoes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you happily sign those documents \Nif {\i1}you{\i0} were kidnapped?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.97,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, their school's prefects \Nwould have our heads!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, figures that's a no-go.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.31,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, please take this even a little seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.69,0:05:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayane. I have an even better idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.73,0:05:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, second-year Sunaookami Shiroko{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We rob a bank.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's bank robbery?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.66,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's guaranteed to get results.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.78,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hit the First Central Bank downtown.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already found \Nthe vault and the guard patrol routes,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.21,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I even figured out the route \Nthe transport car usually takes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, masks. {Short, punchy --ik} {keep  --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! Did you make these yourself, Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We could join the WWE with these! {I was thinking lucha libre but this works too -- ik} {either or --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you came prepared, Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo boy, now we're talking.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right. It's go big or go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Serika{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me the heck outta this!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.11,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not! Criminal activity is off the table!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pout all you want, Shiroko{**-san}, but no means no!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.91,0:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone. \NWe need good, {\i1}reasonable{\i0} ideas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Me next!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Go ahead, second-year Izayoi Nonomi{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.67,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And please, no scams or illegal activities.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My idea is neither a crime nor a scam!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely clean and 100% reliable!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.76,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi{**-senpai}...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.97,Default,,350,0,0,shenan,The secret is... {\alpha&HFF&}Idols!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.26,Default,,350,0,0,shenan,The secret is... Idols!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We become school idols!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Idols?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart and soul of any school \Nrevival arc hinges on idols! {I am heartbroken we're not inserting a love live reference here -- ik} {i have not seen love live but we should --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If all of us break into the pop industry...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.78,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I already came up with a pose and everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}anyone{\i0} taking this seriously?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not getting anywhere like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Hey, hey{*Nya, nya}, Ayane{**-chan}. {Damn, it rhymes too... -ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.67,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we let the teacher decide?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, {*}Teach{*Sensei},
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had to pick one of our ideas, \Nwhich one would it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bank robbery. All the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. Hijacking a bus is clearly better.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I much prefer the idol idea myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.48,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I-If I {\i1}have{\i0} to choose, maybe the ido—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.15,0:07:40.94,Alt,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.65,0:07:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\pos(960,1045)\fscx110\fscy110\xbord8\c&H000000&\1a&H50&\3a&H80&\blur4}Would you please
Dialogue: 11,0:07:45.65,0:07:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\pos(960,1046)\fscx110\fscy110\bord0\shad0\blur2}Would you please
Dialogue: 11,0:07:45.65,0:07:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\pos(960,1047)\fscx110\fscy110\bord0\shad0\blur2}Would you please
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,quit messing around!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.99,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, Ayane{**-chan}'s mad...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Target secured.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aru{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.46,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we {\i1}really{\i0} have to go that far \Njust to recover some stolen goods?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.72,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Refer to me as "Boss" while \Nwe're on the job, Chief of Staff Mutsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.14,0:08:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifices are inevitable in the pursuit \Nof completing a request.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go fretting over every little egg.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're outlaws. It comes with the territory.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.28,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Aru{**-chan}'s doing her thing again.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it, Section Chief Kayoko?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.83,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to confirm, the client demanded \Nthe target be unharmed, didn’t they?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wh-wh-wha?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, does this mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wh-wh-wh-wha—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can kiss our payout goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-wh-wha—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.52,0:09:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?! {### petzku can you think of any fun memes here?}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, Ayane{**-chan}. We're sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my treat, so stop being angry, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}not{\i0} angry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let's wipe that cute little mouth.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you stop patronising me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.54,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane, want more chashu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. {I think it'd be funnier if she just immediately says "yes" after complaining about being patronised -- ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How many in your party?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.42,0:09:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, c-could I please ask how much \Nthe c-cheapest item on the m-menu is?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.09,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be the Shiba Seki Ramen for 580 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our signature dish. I highly recommend it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, th-thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.39,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}, their signature ramen \Nis apparently 580 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, a place where something \Ncosts less than 600 yen!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Every problem has a solution. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all part of the plan!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.20,0:09:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Party of four? I'll show you to your seat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to. We're only ordering for one.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take it to-go.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You may as well be comfortable.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of tables.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, you're so sweet.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist, we'll gladly take you up on that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, while we're at it, could you get us \Nfour pairs of chopsticks? Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.85,0:10:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-You're not planning on splitting \Na single bowl between the four of you, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.48,0:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I'm s-so sorry we're poor!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that's nothing worth apologising over!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.61,0:10:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean it! Without money, \Nwe're just a waste of oxygen!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even deserve to be alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lower than dirt.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being the scum of the earth!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, you're making a scene.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Being poor is nothing to be ashamed of!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.75,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.08,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn straight! Ev'ry dog \Nwill have his moment in the sun. {I've never heard this idiom before so not sure how many people will understand this has to do with money and that everyone has a chance, and it's used to comfort broke people - sikha}{### How's this, if we wanna keep dog here (because it's the dog saying this)?} {Is "every dog has his day" not common usage? Not as familiar with this one --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls are students, aintcha?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'all still scrounged up enough \Nto share a bowl o' ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right chuffed! {I'm shocked this made it through. English Shiba Seki confirmed? --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.85,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit tight, y'hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.81,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like he got the wrong idea about us.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not like we're out begging on the streets. {Well, they ARE broke, but they're not USUALLY this broke. Nuance lost here. -- ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we wanna point fingers, \NAru{**-chan} was the one who blew all our cash.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.57,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did that last job end up being a complete wash,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.40,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but now we've sunk almost all our money \Ninto hiring goons for our next job.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.12,0:11:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, I made sure we had enough for ramen!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This was well within my expectations.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.79,0:11:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, is our next target really so dangerous \Nthat it warrants us starving now? {###} {maybe just "warrants all this" since she's not actually that hung up over the food. In fact, pretty much everyone in PS68 trusts Aru wholeheartedly, but they (read: Mutsuki) just love to mess with her -- ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Aru{**-chan} doesn't even know herself!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she spent all our cash—\Nbecause she's chicken!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a chicken?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure is {\i1}never{\i0} an option.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.06,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We make full use every resource available to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Problem Solver 68's motto!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first I'm hearing about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. She clearly made it up on the spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,1400,0,shenan,{\q2}What on earth?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.32,Default,,1400,0,0,shenan,{\q2}Look at all that ramen!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.12,Default,,800,0,0,shenan,This is enough to feed ten people!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.58,Default,,0,800,0,shenan,Th-This has to be a mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.91,0:12:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, but we couldn't possibly afford this...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly what you ordered, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One regular-sized Shiba Seki ramen for 580 yen!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.38,0:12:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a li'l mishap in the kitchen, y'see?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Figured I may as well, so enjoy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.26,0:12:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see this coming, \Nbut I won't let this goodwill go to waste.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, we'll enjoy it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Aru{**-chan}! Let's dig in already!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.66,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the ramen here just the best?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.08,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell. I've had my fair share \Nof delightful dishes from many restaurants,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.25,0:12:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but ramen {\i1}this{\i0} good is hard to come by.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those uniforms Gehenna's?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a long way from home.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're actually regulars here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.10,0:13:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.06,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kayoko, is it just me, or...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.81,0:13:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're from Abydos High School.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.52,0:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to run into \Nso many kindred souls out here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.78,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes life loves to throw us \Nwonderful surprises, wouldn't you agree? {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you may be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.29,0:13:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she's put two and two together.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.75,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we tell her?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, this is way funnier.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.26,0:13:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope your job goes well.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.93,0:13:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck revitalising your school,.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be rooting for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What great kids, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Department Head Kayoko?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did those uniforms look familiar to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.45,0:14:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No? What about them?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were Abydos High School students.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wha—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They were?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.38,0:14:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see the look on your face!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.76,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But doesn't that mean they're our targets?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I go back and eliminate them?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Way too late for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.64,0:14:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna raid them in a bit anyway,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so save the fun for then, Haruka{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.77,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... There's no way...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those sweethearts are our targets?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"No morals, no mercy."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"We do the crime if you got the dime."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't forget our motto, did you? {"Wasn't that the motto?"}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason to let your emotions \Nget the better of you now. {Maybe "No point overthinking it now" for brevity -- ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.87,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This job's really tearing you apart, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, Aru, get a grip!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the boss of this company! {### "You've got to set an example!"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.59,0:15:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's what you were up to yesterday afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.14,0:15:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And now we're friends \Nwith some students from Gehenna.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.31,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They were super impressed with the boss's ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They were!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised to hear that. It's great.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what were they like?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like they had their own company,{\alpha&HFF&}—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.32,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like they had their own company—{\alpha&HFF&},
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.45,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A security camera captured an armed group \Nadvancing from the south toward the school {My spider sense tells me the word order should be "advancing on the school from the south", but can someone else check in? -- ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the Helmet Gang again?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not them.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.25,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like a group of private mercenaries!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.13,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all prepared?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do as you say, \Nbut we're clocking out on the dot.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since you were stingy with our pay.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the fine print for later!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Prepare to assault Abydos High School!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't those the girls we met at Shiba Seki Ramen?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.81,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, those are the kids from Gehenna \Nwe were talking about earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.78,0:16:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We give you an extra large serving of ramen, \Nand this is how you repay us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We really did appreciate it, \Nbut that was then, and this is now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're on the clock.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Business is business.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we take on a job, we see it to completion.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.42,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. That's how Problem Solver 68 operates!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.26,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you're fixers.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.72,0:16:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! There's more than enough normal, \Nclean part-time jobs students can do!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.31,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a part-time job! \NWe're a real, respectable business!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have titles and everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.07,0:16:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the chief of staff.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's the department head.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.45,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting it like that makes it sound \Neven more fake than it already is. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hired you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.04,0:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's confidential.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just have to make you talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just doing business.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone, let's do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.96,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With you on that one.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up and let us have your school!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.72,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to happen!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kayoko{**-chan}, she's all yours!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going, Mutsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.03,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop your weapon, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good! Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one won't miss.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonating C4.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonating claymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, just in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not looking good.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this on for size!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.09,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're tougher than expected.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.05,0:18:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Keep going! Show them who's boss! {### TLC, please double-check. Pulled this one out of my ass}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.05,0:18:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if we can hold them off for now, \Nthey'll eventually overwhelm us with numbers.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to make a move!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls! I have an idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you hear me out?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.06,0:18:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko. I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine they're just about to break.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the fire until they surrender!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they just getting desperate?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.33,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.63,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done letting you do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop causing problems for us!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They've changed tactics? {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But then they might...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.99,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For what?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.54,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We took on the job, so we'll finish the job, period! {### too much/hamfisted?} {Agreed, dialing it back -- ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.80,0:19:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up and hand over your school!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.97,0:20:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, it's quitting time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all your money buys. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welp, time to go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.42,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so close to winning!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not getting paid, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.51,0:20:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest ain't our problem. Have fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go grab some burgers?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm down!
Comment: 10,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you getting?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.14,0:20:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're mercenaries. \NThey'll stop if the money stops. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they all left.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't do anything about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't we in a pickle.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Aru{**-chan}? Should we run for it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.74,0:21:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't seen the last of us, y'hear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.41,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Aru{**-chan}, you sound like \Na B-movie villain right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.91,0:21:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! We're run—I mean retreating! {This is where I was thinking we could put "We're run" then delete "un" on screen and replace with "We're retreating" for shenanigans -- ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}, wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be seeing you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well they sure were interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.72,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world was all that about?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.10,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're just about done here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go find something to eat?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your treat, right, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.07,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Could I discuss this with my wallet first?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}You're the best{*Thanks}!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.46,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.30,0:23:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears the students of Abydos High School \Nare tougher than the data suggest.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.97,0:23:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of data is all about change. {wordy, but maybe appropriate for how Black Suit tends to talk? -- ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.14,0:23:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But rest assured.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{=3}I will be sure to isolate the cause.

